# Customisation Guide — {{ project_name }}
# Find your goal and follow the arrow.

## LLM PROVIDER
I want to switch LLM provider
  → config.yaml → llm.provider (groq | gemini | azure | ollama)
  → .env → add the new provider's API key (see .env.example)

I want to change the model
  → config.yaml → llm.model

{% if template == 'rag_agent' %}
## RETRIEVAL
I want to retrieve more documents
  → config.yaml → retrieval.top_k (increase, 5-20 recommended)

I want retrieval to match exact keywords better
  → config.yaml → retrieval.hybrid_weight (decrease toward 0.0)

I want to swap ChromaDB for Qdrant
  → rag/vectorstore.py → change provider in get_vectorstore()
  → .env → add QDRANT_URL and QDRANT_API_KEY

## CRAG GRADING
The agent falls back to web search too often
  → config.yaml → crag.incorrect_threshold (decrease toward 0.3)

The agent is accepting bad documents
  → config.yaml → crag.correct_threshold (increase toward 0.95)

I want to change how documents are graded
  → agent/prompts.py → GRADER_PROMPT

{% if include_guards %}
## SECURITY
I want to add a new phrase to block
  → security/input_guard.py → INJECTION_PATTERNS list

I want to redact a new type of PII
  → security/output_guard.py → PII_PATTERNS dict

I want to change the agent's allowed topic scope
  → config.yaml → guards.domain_description
{% endif %}

{% if include_semantic_cache %}
## SEMANTIC CACHE
Cache is returning wrong answers for similar questions
  → config.yaml → semantic_cache.similarity_threshold (increase toward 0.95)

I want to disable caching
  → config.yaml → semantic_cache.enabled: false
{% endif %}
{% endif %}

## OBSERVABILITY
I want to enable Langfuse tracing
  → config.yaml → observability.langfuse: true
  → .env → add LANGFUSE_PUBLIC_KEY and LANGFUSE_SECRET_KEY